## Test File Organization

### Co-location for unit and integration tests

Place test files next to the source file they test:

```
src/
  api/
    assets/
      index.ts          ← production code
      index.test.ts     ← tests for this file
  db/
    utils/
      id.ts
      id.test.ts
  lib/
    rbac.ts
    rbac.test.ts
```

### Separate directory for E2E tests

```
tests/
  e2e/
    auth.test.ts
    asset-create.test.ts
    physical-inventory.test.ts
    reconciliation.test.ts
```

